title: Bug 121687: Exception thrown when exporting data in table inside a grid cell
OB: When attempting to export data in a table that is inside a grid cell, an exception is thrown.
EB: The export functionality should work without throwing an exception when exporting data in a table inside a grid cell.
SR: To reproduce the issue: 1. Insert a grid. 2. Insert a table inside one of the grid cells. 3. Insert another table inside the other grid cell.
